@deps facade, chrome, gui, modalHost

# Invariants & contracts
  @contract  OWNS ps/cm/ds/eventMeta + mm/tm/gm/tv/cmgr + gridPane  @ 3
  @contract  RECEIVES host facade + chrome/gui/modalHost  @ 4
  @contract  checkout take parks on scratch, never slot-registered; close deletes it directly  @ 5
  @contract  bind/unbind pass skipGuard -- the mini stack must never touch the host's guardedTrack  @ 6
  @contract  real gm over an empty groups key -- every edit falls through to tm, wash is empty  @ 7
  @contract  no paramAutomation -- nullPa stands in for tv's structural pa handle  @ 8
  @contract  mini cmgr binds only the pattern-editing keymap subset; rest stay inert  @ 9
  @contract  edits write through on every mini rebuild -- readback strips to the whitelist, deepEq-guarded via the commit callback  @ 10
  @contract  Esc/Cancel restore the open snapshot; Enter/Commit close on the current store  @ 11
  @contract  `armed` gates out the open/close rebuilds  @ 12

